{"tid":2009670,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"康文署運動場淋浴設施明日重開 或考慮人流管制","createTime":"2020-05-10T02:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T02:31:16.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"113a4a76515f3c620d6cc0ab5d746d5cc7aa33e8","tid":2009670,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T02:30:04.000Z","msg":"康文署運動場淋浴設施明日重開 或考慮人流管制<br />\n2020-05-10 HKT 09:40<br />\n<br />\n民政事務局長徐英偉表示，局方近日一直觀察疫情變化，包括過去的長周末，期望盡快放寬更多康文設施。<br />\n<br />\n康文署明日將開放運動場等部分設施，徐英偉於一個電台節目上表示，當局會同時開放部分室內場館的淋浴設施，會隔開使用，亦會考慮人流管制。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，過去一星期包括健身中心等都有放寬措施，重申一直與業界溝通，制訂重開的防疫措施。中小型圖書館將於下一步重新開放，正準備重開的細節；室內泳池等亦希望朝著重開的方向去做，但兒童使用的設施傳播風險較高，可能未會太快放寬。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525266-20200510.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525266-20200510.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpapJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=647f1d60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525266-20200510.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c42da291\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525266-20200510.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"f327317cf0ea78d0cb269da8cd6fba018f8f41cb","tid":2009670,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T02:31:05.000Z","msg":"泳池開未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8faba6ed1d0911d52517991a191e95880089614b","tid":2009670,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T02:31:16.000Z","msg":"康文署好撚污糟嫁"}]}